  "body": " relates to #3610\n\nCurrently we have no facility to easily add metrics in a labelled group that perform as a gauge rather than a counter.\n\nAs a use-case, per-epoch metrics for total attestations, total aggregates, total blocks produced for an epoch would be useful, but this is a gauge, not a counter, as it's going up then back to 0.\n\nAn easy win may be to make SettableGauges under the existing framework, and just have 3 separate gauges rather than a labelled group of gauges, otherwise Besu metrics need to be enhanced to support a labelled gauge.\n",
